pullRequest.body:
Move `succAbove` and `predAbove` to their own file, updating their documentation and adding an `OrderHom` instance for `predAbove`, `predAboveOrderHom`.

---
After ongoing efforts to refactor these two functions, it is now possible to cleanly pull them out into their own file, import
them only when required, and give ourselves more space to add results about them without hitting the space limit.
